<body>
<nav class="breadcrumb">
    <i class="Hui-iconfont"></i>高血压慢病管理 <span class="c-gray en">&gt;</span>风险评估填写
    <a class="btn btn-success radius r" style="line-height:1.6em;margin-top:3px" href="javascript:location.replace(location.href);" title="刷新"><i class="Hui-iconfont">&#xe68f;</i></a>
</nav>
<div class="page-container">
	<input type="hidden" id="order_id" value=""/>
    <form id="hypertension_form">
    	<div class="section">
			<div class="topnav">
				<span style="margin:0 6px;">|</span>
				风险评估
			</div>
			<p>
				<span class="must">*</span>1、年龄是否符合：男性＞55岁、女性＞65岁
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090101" value="0" id="age1"/> 
					<label for="age1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090101" value="1" id="age2"/> 
					<label for="age2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
	        <p>
				<span class="must">*</span>2、是否吸烟
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090201" value="0" id="smoking1"/> 
					<label for="smoking1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090201" value="1" id="smoking2"/> 
					<label for="smoking2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
	       <p>
				<span class="must">*</span>3、血脂是否异常
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090301" value="0" id="blood1"/> 
					<label for="blood1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090301" value="1" id="blood2"/> 
					<label for="blood2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
	        <p>
				<span class="must">*</span>4、是否存在早发心血管疾病家族史
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090401" value="0" id="member1"/> 
					<label for="member1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090401" value="1" id="member2"/> 
					<label for="member2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
	        <p>
				<span class="must">*</span>5、是否属于肥胖体制（体质指数≥28 kg/m2或腹型肥胖：腰围男≥90 cm，女≥85 cm） 
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090501" value="0" id="fei1"/> 
					<label for="fei1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090501" value="1" id="fei2"/> 
					<label for="fei2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
	        <p>
				<span class="must">*</span>6、是否存在靶器官损害
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090601" value="0" id="hart1"/> 
					<label for="hart1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090601" value="1" id="hart2"/> 
					<label for="hart2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
			<p>
				<span class="must">*</span>7、是否合并心脏病、脑血管病、肾脏病、周围血管病、视网膜病变 
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090701" value="0" id="hebing1"/> 
					<label for="hebing1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090701" value="1" id="hebing2"/> 
					<label for="hebing2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
	        <p>
				<span class="must">*</span>8、是否合并糖尿病 
			</p>
			<ul class="contentBox">
				<li style="margin-left: 15px;">
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090801" value="0" id="hetang1"/> 
					<label for="hetang1" class="basicinfo">否</label>
					<input class="" type="radio" name="090801" value="1" id="hetang2"/> 
					<label for="hetang2" class="basicinfo">是</label>
				</li>
	        </ul>
	        <p>
				<span class="must">*</span>9、危险因素
				<input style="margin-left:110px;" class="tetbox" type="number" name="090901"/> <span class="mond">次/分</span>
			</p>
			<p><span class="must">*</span>疾病风险评估
				<select name="risk" class="sel_op" style="margin-left: 103px;">
					<option value="">请选择</option>
					<option value="2500001">低危</option>
					<option value="2500002">中危</option>
					<option value="2500003">高危</option>
					<option value="2500004">很高危</option>
				</select>
			</p>
		</div>
		 
	     <p class="final"><button class="btn btn-danger radius goback">返回</button><button class="btn btn-success radius save">保存</button></p>
    </form>
</div>
